<br>
Fight your way past the first 8 warriors,  then you'll come across 1 wandering elemental crusader, a stationary warrior and crusader guarding the hallway, and a stationary rock golem and crusader right before the dropoff.  Basically you can just fight your way to the rock golem, which can be single pulled at 54 away from the crusader nexto to him.  Then just sit at the rock there and pull the last 5 spawns.  Sometimes the warrior will be green, but the rest should always be blue.<br>
<br>
